name: Friday Night Funkin' But I Wanna Die (Anniversary Edition)
name_original: Friday Night Funkin' But I Wanna Die (Anniversary Edition)
description:
(Having Psych Engine is required to play this mod! Download it here: https://gamebanana.com/mods/309789)

My very first FNF Mod is 1 year old, so I made a Psych Engine port that's just as faithful to the original mod. The plot is basically the same as the original mod. FNF but in a parallel universe where copyright laws don't exist.
